Make a working directory, From your home folder run this command

$ mkdir -p ~/bin
$ mkdir -p ~/android/slimbean

Allow the repo to be executed

$ chmod a+x ~/bin/repo

Install the repository

$ curl https://dl-ssl.google.com/dl/googlesource/git-repo/repo > ~/bin/repo

Change directories

$ cd android/slimbean/

Initialize the manifest

$ repo init -u git://github.com/SlimRoms/platform_manifest.git -b jb